{"tid":1081471,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條女 同我一齊之前 同一個fd既男仔fd 單獨去旅行 ， 但聲稱無發生關係","createTime":"2019-03-28T09:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T21:23:49.000Z","uid":175215,"like":1,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"325041c2419a7db238b6a78f5b82a33342c5bf21","tid":1081471,"uid":175215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:57:23.000Z","msg":"條女一路以來都有好多關於ex既野呃過我， 不過到後期比人踢爆左先坦白。仲要分幾次先黎坦白曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過最後我都選擇相信。 選擇去接受，因為人人都有過去<br />\n<br />\n但最近突然問佢單身果時去旅行同邊個去， 佢先同我坦白呢件事 ，話同一個女仔fd 既男仔fd 單獨去（本身唔熟）， 因為個男仔咁岩分左手。不過果時佢都係單身既。所以都無話邊個錯。<br />\n<br />\n問題係佢話同個男仔咩都無發生過， 大部份日子都係分開玩， 各位師兄覺得信唔信得過？<br />\n我驚佢係人地sp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a213c9324e76b8993ecdb145096b49edf93b86","tid":1081471,"uid":41992,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:59:24.000Z","msg":"唔會係sp  旅行個陣已經屌厭啦"},{"pid":"18bfbe18d904755872e4d5033b202582842225d6","tid":1081471,"uid":162344,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"同你一齊前既事就唔會再計啦，果時又唔識你，做咩都唔關你事"},{"pid":"260d53b341c25d45a4223c5df084ae5474de4077","tid":1081471,"uid":113922,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"之前關你撚事"},{"pid":"e55922014007103d1b9b3b74e2b693b36153c554","tid":1081471,"uid":155628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:11:40.000Z","msg":"你咪信佢冇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw你最多咪食人口水尾"},{"pid":"224b96fe03c0d16c6d89d4b7bf025f2fef2a0cea","tid":1081471,"uid":175215,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"18bfbe18d904755872e4d5033b202582842225d6","tid":1081471,"uid":162344,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"同你一齊前既事就唔會再計啦，果時又唔識你，做咩都唔關你事"},"citedBy":4,"re